; Regression test: Multi-posting lot boundary crossing
;
; Bug: When a transaction has multiple postings reducing the same commodity
; with empty {} cost specs, and processing them crosses lot boundaries,
; rustledger would fail with E4001 "No matching lot" on the second posting.
;
; Root cause: The booking engine was previewing each posting against the
; original inventory instead of the updated state after previous postings.
;
; Example: A crypto sale with a separate fee posting where together they
; exhaust one lot and continue into the next.

option "operating_currency" "USD"

2020-01-01 open Assets:Crypto:Exchange  ADA,USD  "FIFO"
2020-01-01 open Equity:Opening
2020-01-01 open Income:Trading
2020-01-01 open Expenses:Fees

; Lot 1: 100 ADA at $0.50 (oldest)
2021-01-01 * "Opening balance - Lot 1"
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange   100 ADA {0.50 USD, 2021-01-01}
  Equity:Opening          -50 USD

; Lot 2: 100 ADA at $0.52 (newer)
2022-05-19 * "Opening balance - Lot 2"
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange   100 ADA {0.52 USD, 2022-05-19}
  Equity:Opening          -52 USD

; First sale: consume half of lot 1 (50 ADA remaining in lot 1)
2022-05-20 * "Sell 50 ADA"
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange   25 USD
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange  -50 ADA {} @ 0.50 USD
  Income:Trading

; CRITICAL TEST: Two postings in same transaction crossing lot boundary
; - First posting: -75 ADA {} takes 50 from lot 1 + 25 from lot 2
; - Second posting: -5 ADA {} should take from lot 2 (not fail!)
;
; Cost breakdown:
; - 50 ADA from lot 1 @ $0.50 = $25.00
; - 25 ADA from lot 2 @ $0.52 = $13.00
; - 5 ADA from lot 2 @ $0.52 = $2.60
; Total cost basis = $40.60
2022-05-22 * "Sell 80 ADA with fee (crosses lot boundary)"
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange   -75 ADA {}  ; Main sale - crosses lot boundary
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange    -5 ADA {}  ; Fee in-kind (THIS WOULD FAIL before fix)
  Assets:Crypto:Exchange  40.60 USD    ; Proceeds = cost basis (no gain/loss)
  Income:Trading

; If the fix works, inventory should have 70 ADA remaining (all in lot 2)
2022-05-23 balance Assets:Crypto:Exchange  70 ADA
